# SOUND SETTING

Make changes to camera sounds.

To access sound settings, press **MENU/OK**, select the !SET UP Icon (SET UP) tab, and choose **SOUND SET-UP**.

!Sound Setting Menu

## AF BEEP VOL.

Choose the volume of the beep that sounds when the camera focuses. The beep can be muted by selecting **OFF**.

| Options  |        |
|----------|--------|
| !High Volume Icon (high) | !Medium Volume Icon (medium) |
| !Low Volume Icon (low) | !Mute Icon **OFF** (mute) |

## SELF-TIMER BEEP VOL.

Choose the volume of the beep that sounds while the self-timer is active. The beep can be muted by selecting **OFF**.

| Options  |        |
|----------|--------|
| !High Volume Icon (high) | !Medium Volume Icon (medium) |
| !Low Volume Icon (low) | !Mute Icon **OFF** (mute) |
